tion\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, TLTay said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut they have been good enough to us to give us Friday updates for free!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpeaking of which.... Its almost FRIDAY!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-15T01:52:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs we pointed out the last time this question was asked, there\u0027s no reason to be nasty to the people asking. Some comments have been removed, now please move on to other discussions.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}